title: 271: Rhett Surprises His Wife For Her Birthday | Ear Biscuits Ep.271
description:
"I've never enjoyed a gift given to someone else more than how much I enjoyed the gift that you gave Jessie" - Link Neal, 2021. And it's not the Jason Momoa photobook. Listen to R&L talk about Rhett's surprise birthday gift for Jessie that had Link raving on this episode of Ear Biscuits!
